Demonstation for usage of MediaInfo Library:

https://mediaarea.net/de/MediaInfo

With java/jna binding from 

https://github.com/UniversalMediaServer/UniversalMediaServer/blob/2d63630d25faafae34f4eaad7f06062647b29d0c/src/main/java/net/pms/dlna/MediaInfo.java

This is purely for demonstration. For redistribution, please refer to the
two referenced projects.